OL,3,CEx-Spurs chairman Levy says he will
OL,4,Cfeel 'emptiness' if team gets relegated
OL,6,FWords by Senior Sports Producer Joe
OL,7,FWardropper
OL,9,FFormer Tottenham Hotspur chairman
OL,10,FDaniel Levy says he will feel an
OL,11,F"emptiness in the stomach" if the team
OL,12,Fare relegated from the Premier League
OL,13,Fthis season.
OL,15,FSpeaking for the first time since
OL,16,Fabruptly stepping down in September
OL,17,Fafter 24 years in charge at Spurs,
OL,18,FLevy told ITV News he still watched
OL,19,F"every match" and that a loss "ruins
OL,20,Fthe whole weekend".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
