OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778699494
OL,3,CEx-Spurs chairman Levy says he will
OL,4,Cfeel 'emptiness' if team gets relegated
OL,6,FWith just two games left to play,
OL,7,FTottenham, who have started every
OL,8,Fseason in the topflight since the
OL,9,Fleague's creation in 1992, are only
OL,10,Ftwo points clear of the drop zone.
OL,12,FBut Levy - who was at Buckingham
OL,13,FPalace on Wednesday to receive a CBE
OL,14,Ffor services to charity and community
OL,15,F- said he was "optimistic" that Spurs
OL,16,Fwould avoid falling into the
OL,17,FChampionship.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778699494
OL,3,CEx-Spurs chairman Levy says he will
OL,4,Cfeel 'emptiness' if team gets relegated
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"I'm optimistic that we will remain in
OL,12,Fthe Premier League. I think Tottenham
OL,13,Fhas a great coach, and all the fans
OL,14,Fand all the employees and everyone now
OL,15,Fis behind this coach... Let's hope
OL,16,Fthat the players can do it for the
OL,17,Flast two games."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
