PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778699494
OL,3,CEx-Spurs chairman Levy says he will
OL,4,Cfeel 'emptiness' if team gets relegated
OL,6,FRobert de Zerbi's side missed a
OL,7,Fcrucial opportunity to go four points
OL,8,Fclear of relegation rivals West Ham on
OL,9,FMonday, after only picking up a draw
OL,10,Fagainst Leeds United.
OL,12,F"Like every fan", Levy added,
OL,13,Frelegation would leave him with an
OL,14,F"emptiness in the stomach. But we will
OL,15,Fbounce back. Let's be optimistic and
OL,16,Fhope that doesn't happen."
OL,18,F"I just hope at this moment in time
OL,19,Fthat Tottenham manages to remain in
OL,20,Fthe Premier League."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
