OL,3,CEx-Spurs chairman Levy says he will
OL,4,Cfeel 'emptiness' if team gets relegated
OL,6,FLevy was presented with the honour by
OL,7,FPrince William, and joked that they
OL,8,Fdiscussed football, the forthcoming
OL,9,FWorld Cup, and Aston Villa, the
OL,10,FPrince's beloved team.
OL,12,F"I thanked him very well for allowing
OL,13,Fus to beat Aston Villa a few weeks
OL,14,Fago," Levy said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
