OL,3,CEx-Spurs chairman Levy says he will
OL,4,Cfeel 'emptiness' if team gets relegated
OL,6,FAsked about the highlights of his time
OL,7,Fat Spurs, the 64-year-old said: "I was
OL,8,Fthere for over 24 years and we had so
OL,9,Fmany memorable occasions, the
OL,10,FChampions League final, early on,
OL,11,Fbeing in Europe many years, opening
OL,12,Fthe stadium, there have been so many
OL,13,Fachievements."
